{"tid":1408443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罷個工又有乜用啫？","createTime":"2019-08-04T17:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T17:33:10.000Z","uid":242393,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"531eb36ab8e54b6845a3a8ce278867dc4bd4a7f0","tid":1408443,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:19:50.000Z","msg":"唔明點解罷個工<br />\n一件咁簡單、外國成日見到既事<br />\n但係香港就要搞到咁勞師動眾<br />\n<br />\n點解香港people's power可以細到咁<br />\n香港市民完全無可以同政府bargain既本錢<br />\n罷佢老尾一日之後<br />\n係咪所有野都要回復基本步？<br />\n係咪要繼續做馴民？<br />\n係咪繼續比警黑治港？<br />\n<br />\n好多野諗，愈諗愈唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係！呢兩個月出現咁多政治醜惡同不公義但<br />\n呢個時候已經<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">別無他選</span></strong></span><br />\n8.5 香港人無論如何一定要站！出！來！<br />\n罷工罷課罷市 + 罷買 + 集會！！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">等我哋聽日打一場靚仗</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"a9a24bf337d72598b58be8c558371a450f807615","tid":1408443,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:20:48.000Z","msg":"訓唔到，幫推"},{"pid":"9f1bcc594ffcd76330b196f8519664fbb72a774a","tid":1408443,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263378e2b5973496b66ded9d85d7d568cd100b97","tid":1408443,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif